## 🔄 Alur Data ETL

```
monitor_log_datatransaksi (raw transaksi)
    ↓ [ETL Pipeline]
    Slot mapping + variant mapping
    Agregasi harian (demand per tanggal/shift/varian)
    Flag is_holiday, is_weekend, is_ramadan
    ↓
Vending_Aggregrated (clean daily data)
    ↓ [ML Feature Builder]
    build_v3_exact_features() → CSV temp
    ↓
vending_training_ml (ML-ready features)
    ↓ [Forecast Service]
    XGBoost predict → ForecastResults_Layer1
    Statistical distribute → ForecastResults_Layer2
```

**Catatan Penting ETL**: Hanya data sistem (is_manual_insert = 0) yang di-delete/regenerasi. Data yang diinput manual admin (is_manual_insert = 1) tetap aman.

